<P>
   OBIT-CADMUS (Undated) _ Paul Cadmus, an American artist noted
for a virtuosic figurative style that he applied to subjects
ranging from biting social satire to moralizing allegories to often
sentimental male nudes, died on Sunday at his home in Weston, Conn.
He was 94. By Holland Cotter.
</P>
