Atlanta Journal-Constitution).
</P>
<P>
   SHOPPING-DESTINATION _ A weekly feature about fun places to shop
in the Southeast. This week: Shopping on King St. in Charleston, S.
C. Also, a list of some restaurants and where to stay in this city.
(MJohnson, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 25.
</P>
<P>
   NEWS-QUESTIONS _ Q&AMP;A on the news, in two takes. (Bessonnette,
Atlanta Journal-Constitution)
</P>
<P>
   EDs: Moving on (l) Lifestyle and (a) General News categories.
MOVED.
