<P>
   ENTERTAINMENT-ARTS
</P>
<P>
   KAYKYSER _ ROCKY MOUNT, N.C. _ Mortarboard Productions, in
association with the North Carolina Museum of Art Foundation, will
produce ``Kay Kyser _ A Life in Motion.'' It will document the life
of Kyser from his days as head cheerleader at UNC Chapel Hill
through more than two decades as a big band leader, host of
``College of Musical Knowledge'' and a movie star. At his peak, he
walked away from stardom. (Moran, Rocky Mount Telegram). MOVED.
