<P>
   Not employed...........................32
</P>
<P>
   16. How satisfied are you with your job?
</P>
<P>
   (Based on Employed Respondents)
</P>
<P>
   Very satisfied.........................47
</P>
<P>
   Somewhat satisfied.....................41
</P>
<P>
   Somewhat dissatisfied...................8
</P>
<P>
   Very dissatisfied.......................4
</P>
<P>
   17. What's the greatest pleasure you get from working -- the
salary you take home, or the satisfaction you get from the job
itself?
</P>
<P>
   Salary..................................23
</P>
<P>
   Satisfaction............................66
</P>
<P>
   Both equal...............................9
</P>
