against Linda Tripp. By Neil A. Lewis.
</P>
<P>
   LA-POLICE-SCANDAL (Los Angeles) _ Authorities now say a police
scandal here may have tainted as many as 3,000 cases. Developing.
By Todd S. Purdum.
</P>
<P>
   SF-MAYORAL (San Francisco) _ Folo on Willie Brown's victory in
the mayoral runoff. By Evelyn Nieves.
</P>
<P>
   GM-MADD (Detroit) _ General Motors announces donation to Mothers
Against Drunk Driving. By Robyn Meredith.
</P>
<P>
   NY-TRANSIT (New York) _ Details of the transit workers contract
settlement averting a strike. By Steven Greenhouse.
