r v BC-TEXBUDGET-TEX     12-15 0430
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-TEXBUDGET-TEX </SLUG>
 
 
<TEXT>
<P>
   The Fort Worth Star-Telegram plans to move the following stories
for clients of the NYTimes News Service for AMs and PMs of
Thursday, Dec. 16, and thereafter. If you have any questions,
please call Tom Uhler, Lou Hudson, Carmelita Bevill or Jim Peipert
on the Star-Telegram's National/Foreign Desk at (817) 390-7785. &QL; 
 &QL; 
 &QL;
</P>
<P>
   (Visit the Star-Telegram's online services on the World Wide
Web: www.star-telegram.com) &QL; 
 &QL; 
 &QL; 
 &QL;
</P>
<P>
   Fort Worth Star-Telegram News Budget for Wednesday, Dec. 15,
1999. Star-Telegram National/Foreign Desk: 817-390-7784/85.
(Editors: Carmelita Bevill, Tom Uhler, Lou Hudson and Jim Peipert)
 &QL; 
 &QL;
