<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-12-15 18:41 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A0015 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u s BC-SKI-WEATHER-BOS &LR;      12-15 1751
