<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-12-15 19:16 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A0046 &Cx1f; ttj-z
u a BC-TEXAS-EXECUTIONS-HNS &LR;      12-15 0673
</HEADER>
<BODY>
