   BBA-REDSOX-TRADE (Undated) _ Red Sox, Houston Astros trade
Everetts -- Carl for Adam. Switch-hitting outfielder Carl Everett
goes to Boston for shortstop prospect Adam Everett and leftie
pitcher Greg Miller. By Gordon Edes. 800 words.
