</HEADLINE>
 
 This ``separate buy'' article is from Latin Trade magazine,
America's leading journal of Latin American business, finance and
trade: &HT;    MILKING THE MILLENNIUM AT THE HOTTEST LATIN AMERICAN HOT-SPOTS.
Airlines, cruise lines, hotels _ just about all industries _ are
raising rates through the roof for the party of a lifetime. Will
anybody go? And where are the hottest Latin American hot-spots?
 &HT;    Filed as BC-MILLENNIUM-HOT-SPOTS-LATINTRADE-NYTSF in ``f''
financial, ``l'' lifestyle y ``t'' travel.
