<HEADLINE>
ANOTHER WASTED SHOT IN THE DARK 
</HEADLINE>
   (For use by N.Y. Times News Service clients)  
 By E.J. MONTINI  
 c.1999 The Arizona Republic  
<TEXT>
<P>
   One warm summer evening last June, for reasons we don't know, a
